dc_description_s: Map shows House of Representative and Senate constituency district boundaries; municipal, village, and concession boundaries; three categories of roads, railroads; telegraph lines; cemeteries, qubba, wadis. Includes index listing s of House of Representatives and Senate constituencies. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "Jan. 1952 (Topo. No. S. 881-52) ; Topo. No. S. 963-57." "Note; The detail of this sheet is compiled from cadastral, town and topographical surveys adjusted to triangulation stations. Other information is added from air photographs."
